#!/bin/bash
set -e

# Challenge 3 Setup: Infrastructure Resources
echo "Setting up Challenge 3: Infrastructure Resources..."

# Clean workspace
cd /root/terraform-lab
terraform destroy -auto-approve 2>/dev/null || true
rm -rf *

# Copy example solution from GitHub repo to solutions directory
mkdir -p /root/terraform-lab-solutions/challenge-03
cp -r /root/lab-assets/assets/challenge-03/* /root/terraform-lab-solutions/challenge-03/

# Return to workspace
cd /root/terraform-lab

# Display welcome message
cat << 'EOF'

╔════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
║                                                                ║
║            Challenge 3: Infrastructure Resources               ║
║                                                                ║
╚════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝

In this challenge, you'll build a complete 3-tier infrastructure:

  • Virtual Network with NAT and DHCP
  • Storage Pools and Volumes
  • Three VMs (web, app, database)
  • Resource dependencies

📁 Working Directory: /root/terraform-lab
📚 Example Solution: /root/terraform-lab-solutions/challenge-03

Follow the instructions in the assignment to complete the challenge!

EOF

echo "Challenge 3 setup complete!"

